| `page_number` | Page metadata |
| `year` | Year metadata |
| `theme` | Theme metadata |

---

### 3.5 Step 4 — Build Vector Store

Module:

```text
src/agro_rag/rag/vector_store.py
```

Main function:

```python
build_vector_store_from_chunks()
```

Purpose:

```text
document chunks
→ embeddings
