## 6. Application Workflow

The Streamlit app connects the user interface to the RAG pipeline.

App file:

```text
app/streamlit_app.py
```

Run command:

```bash
streamlit run app/streamlit_app.py
```

App workflow:

```text
user question
→ optional source filter
→ vector retrieval
→ retrieved chunks
→ optional LLM answer
→ answer + evidence display
```

The app supports:

- MapBiomas / INPE evidence retrieval;
- retrieval-only mode;
- LLM-based RAG mode;
- source filtering;
- inspection of retrieved chunks;
- display of execution metadata.

